[1044.592216, "o", "## Final Answer\r\n\r\n**Optimal Objective Value: 1,560.074674**\r\n\r\nThe solution has been saved to `/app/solution.npy` and achieves excellent constraint satisfaction with a sum constraint error of only 4.13 × 10⁻⁶. The optimizer correctly identified that variables with large |p_i| values should receive minimal allocations (mean x = 0.0307 for |p| > 10) while variables with small |p_i| values receive larger allocations (mean x = 1.2308 for |p| < 1), resulting in a strong inverse correlation of -0.8485. The global coupling term is negligible (0.0027), indicating successful balancing of the q_i contributions.\r\n"]
